data.description: Stunning home in Montereau! This home is better than new with over $20k in improvements already included! The floorplan offers 4 bedrooms downstairs or 3 bedrooms and an office, an upstairs bonus room, mudroom, 3 full baths & 3 car garage. The upstairs bonus has a full bath so you have the optional extra living space or bedroom. As you enter the home you’re immediately drawn to the vaulted cathedral living room ceiling with wood beam accent and brick to ceiling fireplace. The kitchen features a large center island, custom cabinets, quartz countertops & breakfast bar, pantry, and builtin SS appliances w/gas range. Spacious Master bedroom & Ensuite with free standing tub, oversized walk-in shower, dbl vanities, and the utility room is connected to master closet for convenience. Laundry room offers great storage with wash sink and matching Quartz counters. Additional upgrades and improvements include full home gutter system, new privacy fence that is unshared by neighbors, HG Polyaspartic Floor Coating on the garage floors, and gas supply for grill at the back patio. The neighborhood offers a pool, clubhouse & playground. Don’t miss out on an opportunity to see this home!
